canonical_structure.name: UBX-RXM-MEASD12
canonical_structure.description: Satellite measurements for CloudLocate location service (first 12 bytes message)

issues: Failed to identify fixed count of 12 as indicated by the message name (MEASD12)

adjudication.reasoning: The message UBX-RXM-MEASD12 is specifically designed to transmit the first 12 bytes of satellite measurement data for the u-blox CloudLocate service. The '12' in the message name is a definitive indicator of its fixed payload length. Extraction 1 correctly identifies the fixed length of 12 bytes. Extraction 2 incorrectly models the message as having variable length 'N', which is likely a halluncination based on other RXM-MEAS variants (like MEASX) which are indeed variable length.
